{"tid":1648311,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"成日話要民主民主，係民主制度trump唔係唯一既權力","createTime":"2019-10-12T06:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T10:40:10.000Z","uid":104138,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9050a0b6c09fa9a2d8de4cc2c361b1db3da60cf3","tid":1648311,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:52:20.000Z","msg":"成日見trump 講咩衰野就無晒士氣，我屌你地班成日要民主既人<br />\n係民主國家總統唔一定話晒事，一日仲有國會支持我地就係上風<br />\n更何況trump 呢個人成日彈出彈入，講既野信住一半先啦<br />\n<br />\n成日話爭取民主，如果你要睇總統頭，鄰國就岩晒你<br />\n我地唔係要一個人統治我地，我地係要一個政府同人民可以互相制衡既制度，所以唔好再因為民主國家總統講咩就覺得一定輸<br />\n<br />\n英國都係，政府唔做野唔代表輸硬，議員支持既話一樣可以迫到政府做野"},{"pid":"77851091ea7fa05f1547402f3cb539cc85e1de1f","tid":1648311,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59b5967f735071f70be8ee007e7cae5b6e46653","tid":1648311,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T06:54:56.000Z","msg":"又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地老侵踏遍美國黑暗商界70年，習近平憑咩同人打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n封頂公會會長 vs 小圈毒撚隊長"},{"pid":"4e23a2aa8a83462afc1b4c733a13ff13482d7a35","tid":1648311,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"［核彈行動］令警察家變！針對警妻開闢新文宣線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647500</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情請睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647500</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"728e032d8df310a203285db83daf75a1e1d7a4ca","tid":1648311,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r